item.title: CVE-2021-24901|2024-08-03T19:49:13.923Z -- unknown -- security%20audit
item.description: The Security Audit WordPress plugin through 1.0.0 does not sanitise and escape the Data Id setting, which could allow high privilege users to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
